        "text": "Hq Co - 66th Med Tk Bn\n2d Armored Division, Cp Hood, Texas\nOccupation and hobbies:\nOfficer.\nComments of Interrogator relative to intelligence and character of\nobserver (Check neighbors, police dept., FBI records, employer, etc.):\nObserver had difficulty explaining in detail what he saw.\nDEGRADED/UNCLASSIFIED\nMAY 26 1976\nON\nBY FEP CDR USAINSCOM\nAUTH Para 1-303 DOD\nDid observer wear glasses, especially polarized glasses at time of\nsighting, or was object viewed through canopy, window, or other\ntransparent material? None.\nPages 3 & 4 of this form not applicable to this incident.\nInterviewed by:\nGeorge M. Livers\nCONFIDENTIAL\nCONFIDENTIAL\nCaptain, Inf"
